    <div class="aboutWSS">
        <p>Ultra short stories are unique literary creations.
            <p>A well written one-liner story provides the reader with a quick
                yet thought
                provoking piece of literature that coax the imagination to populate the imperative voids, thereby
                becoming
                part
                of the creative mechanism. They are not tales with punchlines, but rather the punchlines themselves that
                force the mind to generate the tale in a process of reversal.</p>
        </p>
        <p>For the writer, an ultra short story presents
            different challenges than other types of story-telling. In one swift stroke they need to
            convey the setting, the characters and the plot, leaving any conflicts and their resolution to form in
            the imagination.</p>
        <p>In short, they are a lot of fun to write, and a great pleasure to read!</p>
    </div>

